22
00:01:16,606 --> 00:01:17,909
All right, back up!

23
00:01:17,909 --> 00:01:18,978
Give him some room.

24
00:01:18,979 --> 00:01:20,048
Come on, clear out.

25
00:01:20,049 --> 00:01:22,354
Back up.

26
00:01:22,355 --> 00:01:25,497
Al.

27
